> #### Short-term plans:
>
> - Fixing CMake
> - Preparing headers etc. for Qt6

> #### Mid-term plans:
>
> - Barebones port to Qt6
> - Implementing upstream changes in source files that use RtAudio (mainly soapySDR)
> - Implementing misc upstream changes in drm_pulseaudio, drm_portaudio and drm_soapySDR
> - Fixing quirks in the Dream transmitter

> #### Long-term goals:
